IMAPAccount mailbox
Host imap.mailbox.org
User jhk06@mailbox.org
PassCmd "pass show mail/mailbox.org | head -n1"
TLSType IMAPS

IMAPStore mailbox-remote
Account mailbox

MaildirStore mailbox-local
Path ~/mail/
Inbox ~/mail/Inbox

Channel mailbox-inbox
Far :mailbox-remote:INBOX
Near :mailbox-local:INBOX
SyncState *
Expunge Both

Channel mailbox-all
Far :mailbox-remote:
Near :mailbox-local:
Pattern * !INBOX
SyncState *
Create Both

Group mailbox
Channel mailbox-inbox
Channel mailbox-all
